README
------

* hello-world.py: basic flask application saying "Hello, world!"

* hello-world-public.py: basic flask application saying "Hello, world!
  Nice to see you!". Available for general public, debug mode enabled, 
  and reloading automatically if code changes.

-- flask microblog example --

* flask-microblog.py: a microblog application based on flask

* schema.sql: sql statement to create the initial microblog database
